    "Furthermore, dependency management plays a critical role in this step, as modern software often relies heavily on third-party code, such as external libraries, to streamline development processes [115].",
    "However, this practice can introduce dependency vulnerabilities [169], underscoring the importance of effectively managing external libraries and dependencies to ensure the reliability and security of the software product.",
    "For instance, Dependabot [69] in GitHub helps users monitor their software dependencies and issues security alerts to users if finding vulnerable dependencies.Build, Test, and Deployment.",
